            "title": "Oceaneering Non-GAAP EPS of $0.30 misses by $0.03, revenue of $692M beats by $20.65M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Oceaneering <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20484284-oceaneering-reports-first-quarter-2026-results\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OII\" title=\"Oceaneering International, Inc.\">OII</a></span>): Q1 Non-GAAP EPS of $0.30 <span> misses by $0.03</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $692M (+2.6% Y/Y) <span> beats by $20.65M</span>.</li>\n<li><ul>\n<li>Operating income was $57.8 million, a decrease of 21%.</li>\n<li>Net income was $36.1 million, a decrease of 28%.</li>\n<li>Adjusted EBITDA was $83.7 million, a decrease of 13%.</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li>Cash Flow<ul>\n<li>Cash flow used in operating activities was $(59.1) million.</li>\n<li>Free cash flow was $(76.5) million.</li>\n<li>Quarter-end cash and cash equivalents totaled $607 million, compared to $382 million at the end of the same period last year.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
