            "id": "4578329",
            "title": "Astra Exploration upsizes private placement to C$13M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Astra Exploration (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASTR:CA\" title=\"Astra Exploration Inc.\">ASTR:CA</a></span>) (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">OTCQB: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ATEPF\" title=\"Astra Exploration Inc.\">ATEPF</a></span>) on Wednesday said it has increased the size of its bought deal private placement to about C$13 million from a previously announced offering.</li>\n<li>The company will issue about 16.9 million shares at C$0.77 each, and has granted underwriters an option to purchase an additional roughly 2.6 million shares, which could raise total proceeds to about C$15 million if fully exercised.</li>\n<li>Astra said it plans to use the proceeds for exploration and development of its La Manchuria project, as well as for general corporate and working capital purposes.</li>\n<li>The offering is expected to close on or about April 30, subject to regulatory approvals, including from the TSX Venture Exchange.<img alt=\"https://rt.newswire.ca/rt.gif?NewsItemId=C9116&amp;Transmission_Id=202604221657CANADANWCANADAPR_C9116&amp;DateId=20260422\" fetchpriority=\"high\" src=\"https://rt.newswire.ca/rt.gif?NewsItemId=C9116&amp;Transmission_Id=202604221657CANADANWCANADAPR_C9116&amp;DateId=20260422\"/>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>ASTR:CA closed <span>+1.19%</span> at $0.85.</li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20484260-astra-exploration-inc-announces-upsize-of-bought-deal-private-placement-to-c-13m\">Press Release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
