            "id": "4578280",
            "title": "ISS says ConocoPhillips shareholders should vote for independent board chair",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\"><span>Proxy advisor Institutional Shareholder Services said Wednesday that ConocoPhillips (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COP\" title=\"ConocoPhillips\">COP</a></span>) </span><span>shareholders should <a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/legal/transactional/proxy-advisor-iss-urges-conocophillips-shareholders-vote-independent-board-chair-2026-04-22/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_self\" title=\"vote in favor\">vote in favor</a> of a proposal calling for an independent board chair, citing ​the need for stronger oversight of management.</span></p>\n<p><span>ISS said it backs the non-binding proposal that asks Conoco (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COP\" title=\"ConocoPhillips\">COP</a>) to separate the roles of chair and CEO, with an independent director holding the board chair position, citing concerns over the current lead director role, which is chosen ​by non-employee directors and not independent directors.</span></p>\n<p><span>\"The board is responsible for ​overseeing management and instilling accountability, and conflicts of interest may arise when ​one person holds both the chairman and CEO positions,\" ISS said.</span></p>\n<p><span><span>ConocoPhillips' (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COP\" title=\"ConocoPhillips\">COP</a>) governance structure is similar to that of Exxon Mobil</span><span> and Chevron, where the CEOs </span><span>⁠also ​serve as chairmen on their respective boards; BP </span>has separate CEO and chairman positions.</span></p>\n<p><span>Conoco's (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COP\" title=\"ConocoPhillips\">COP</a>) board has recommended ​that shareholders ⁠vote against the proposal for an independent board chairman; Ryan Lance currently serves ‌as ⁠both Chairman and CEO.</span></p>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/assets/og_image_1200-29b2bfe1a595477db6826bd2126c63ac2091efb7ec76347a8e7f81ba17e3de6c.png",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4578280-iss-says-conocophillips-shareholders-should-vote-for-independent-board-chair",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 04:55:19",
            "source": "seekalpha",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
